            <note xml:id="n03010801" n="1">
               <name type="person" key="Gibson, George">George Gibson</name> or <name type="person" key="Shannon, George">George Shannon</name> might be meant, but <name type="person" key="Drouillard, George">Drouillard</name> was one of the party's outstanding hunters. Subsequent references to "<name type="person" key="Drouillard, George">George</name>" are probably also to him.</note>
